Camlog tube-in-tube implants were introduced several years ago. This multicenter 
retrospective analysis evaluated the success rate of Root-Line and Screw-Line 
tube-in-tube implants in daily use. A total of 201 implants were placed in 96 
patients with different indications and implantation procedures. Implants were 
analyzed retrospectively after a functional loading period of 12 to 78 months. 
